    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<div class=\"passage\"><div class=\"prose style:1\"><p class=\"passage_para\">A beach community was recently negatively affected by a hurricane. Community leaders are looking for a potential solution to prevent damage from future hurricanes. Below is a list of their concerns as well as how important each issue is to the community.</p></div></div>\n<div class=\"table_wrapper\"><table class=\"tgroup align:center cols:2\">\n<thead class=\"thead\"><tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colname:col1\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Community Concerns</span></th>\n<th class=\"entry colname:col2\"><span class=\"formatted_text font_weight:bold\">Concern Level</span></th>\n</tr></thead>\n<tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Wave action</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Low</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Beachfront development</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Low</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Nearshore aquaculture</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Low</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Health of nearby coral reef</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">Moderate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Roosting bird species</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">High</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colname:col1\">Storm surge threat</td>\n<td class=\"entry colname:col2\">High</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div>\n</div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following solutions would best address the issues of greatest concern in the community?</p>\n",
